law.history: Repealed 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 250, sec. 5, effective July 1, 1960. -- Amended 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 77, Art. 10, secs. 10-107. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 523b-1, 523b-4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Personal property that may be mortgaged, rank of mortgage.
